  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/aa94e996b6058f6b4dff6b80a089d0fd.avif?t=1763150606\" width=610 height=200 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>15 years from now, in the distant year of 1999: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ronald Reagan is midway through his fifth term. Under his economic oversight the rich have gotten richer while, for most of us, the American dream has drifted farther and farther from reach.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Unable to afford healthcare or feed their own families many desperate Americans only have one option left: BloodDome99</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for survival and glory in a blood-drenched arena. Earn money and buy upgrades but be careful- every dollar spent brings you further from your goal: buying your freedom.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >40+ UNIQUE WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/41c63d74bcdb21bb4c9bf84cac9dc24a.poster.avif?t=1763150606\" width=594 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/41c63d74bcdb21bb4c9bf84cac9dc24a.webm?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/41c63d74bcdb21bb4c9bf84cac9dc24a.mp4?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use paper planes, snow blowers, flamethrowers, bee guns, and other inventive arms to mow down the competition. And have fun mixing and matching by simultaneously wielding as many weapons as you can afford</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEBREAKING BUILDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/4f6e78e168aa6c98eef1621908a52d33.poster.avif?t=1763150606\" width=594 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/4f6e78e168aa6c98eef1621908a52d33.webm?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/4f6e78e168aa6c98eef1621908a52d33.mp4?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Become an explosives expert, sniper, tank, ninja... find your playstyle with tons of perks and upgrades</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/aa94e996b6058f6b4dff6b80a089d0fd.avif?t=1763150606\" width=610 height=200 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>15 years from now, in the distant year of 1999: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ronald Reagan is midway through his fifth term. Under his economic oversight the rich have gotten richer while, for most of us, the American dream has drifted farther and farther from reach.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Unable to afford healthcare or feed their own families many desperate Americans only have one option left: BloodDome99</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for survival and glory in a blood-drenched arena. Earn money and buy upgrades but be careful- every dollar spent brings you further from your goal: buying your freedom.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >40+ UNIQUE WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/41c63d74bcdb21bb4c9bf84cac9dc24a.poster.avif?t=1763150606\" width=594 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/41c63d74bcdb21bb4c9bf84cac9dc24a.webm?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/41c63d74bcdb21bb4c9bf84cac9dc24a.mp4?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use paper planes, snow blowers, flamethrowers, bee guns, and other inventive arms to mow down the competition. And have fun mixing and matching by simultaneously wielding as many weapons as you can afford</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEBREAKING BUILDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/4f6e78e168aa6c98eef1621908a52d33.poster.avif?t=1763150606\" width=594 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/4f6e78e168aa6c98eef1621908a52d33.webm?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351890/extras/4f6e78e168aa6c98eef1621908a52d33.mp4?t=1763150606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Become an explosives expert, sniper, tank, ninja... find your playstyle with tons of perks and upgrades</p>",
